pan>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"},{"pid":"c9cf9a600f32ba0a6dce05e2aa3705c3c2b8acb6","tid":2029041,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"924bd918c21840b53b57a2dcc2e0211eeff87e0e","tid":2029041,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%AC%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259C%25BE%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%258E%2588%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=78ae11ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259C%25BE%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%258E%2588%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&h=a529cf8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%AC%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港獨立軍力一定唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />! 如果有🇺🇸美屬香港， 可以部署薩德導彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 仲要唔使錢買<img src=\"/asse